updates.update_content:
I got an update from Dave our production chief and I wanted to share the good news with you. 
All Dead Reckoning Color proofs have been approved and authorized our factories to begin mass production as of today. This means not only cards, but all tokens, punchboard, the cube-tower ship, packaging, and everything else! WoHoo!!!
During the "mass production" step a few other things will happen;

We wanted to start this one off with a simple message. Every one of these updates is to keep you posted on what we are doing NOW, and the checklist should serve as a reminder for what WE need to do before wrapping this up.
Terrain Implementation: We had a few questions on this from our test groups. All the implementations have been cleaned up. Here is comprehensive breakdown of the changes;
Balancing Volume 1: We have gotten into the back half of the Scenarios and cleaning them up. The first scenarios are now being completed. This is a look at what they were when sent to our test group. Next update we should have a finalized look to compare them for you.
